BTTTriggers.BTTPredefinedActionName: Launch Application / Open File / Start Apple Script …

BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString: -- This script can be used in conjunction with Better Touch Tool to display the currently playing track on the MacBook Pro TouchBar-- More info here: https://lucatnt.com/2017/02/display-the-currently-playing-track-in-itunesspotify-on-the-touch-barif application "Spotify" is running then	tell application "Spotify"		if player state is playing then			return (get artist of current track) & " - " & (get name of current track)		else			return ""		end if	end tellelse	return ""end if
